(3, 1, 'Compute Capacity', 'How resilient is your AI compute to energy disruption?', 'No dedicated energy planning for AI workloads', 'Standard commercial energy contracts; no AI-specific provision', 'Dedicated energy supply agreements for data centre / AI operations', 'National grid allocation or renewable energy contracts dedicated to AI', null, 10, 35, 65, 90, null),
(4, 1, 'Compute Capacity', 'How exposed is your AI hardware supply chain to foreign dependency?', '100% dependent on foreign-fabricated chips (no domestic supply chain visibility)', 'Foreign-fabricated but with diversified suppliers and strategic stockpiles', 'Some domestic assembly or packaging; fabrication remains foreign', 'Partial domestic fabrication capability or strategic alliance with fabricator', 'Sovereign fabrication or guaranteed allied-nation supply agreement', 10, 30, 50, 75, 95),
