(6, 2, 'Capital Formation', 'What proportion of your government''s total R&D budget is allocated to AI infrastructure and development?', 'No dedicated AI budget line', '< 1% of total R&D spend', '1–3% of total R&D spend', '3–5% of total R&D spend', '> 5% of total R&D spend', 5, 20, 45, 70, 95),
