(12, 3, 'Regulatory Readiness', 'Is there a national AI governance framework with legal force?', 'No AI-specific governance framework', 'Draft framework or voluntary guidelines only', 'Enacted legislation covering some AI applications', 'Comprehensive AI statute with regulator and enforcement powers', 5, 25, 60, 95),
(13, 3, 'Regulatory Readiness', 'Has your nation designated a lead AI regulator or oversight body?', 'No designated body', 'Working group or informal coordination', 'Designated lead agency with partial mandate', 'Dedicated AI regulator with full licensing and enforcement powers', 5, 30, 60, 95),
(14, 3, 'Regulatory Readiness', 'Do you have sector-specific AI regulations (finance, health, defence, transport)?', 'No sector-specific requirements', '1 sector with AI-specific rules', '2–3 sectors with tailored regulations', 'All critical sectors covered with tailored AI regimes', 5, 35, 65, 95),
