(21, 4, 'Data Sovereignty', 'Does your nation have classified or air-gapped computing environments for strategic AI workloads?', 'No classified or air-gapped AI environments exist', 'Classified environments exist but not configured for AI workloads', 'Classified AI-ready environments with sovereign cloud regions', 'Full trusted operating environment with jurisdictional guarantees and AI integration', 5, 30, 65, 90),
(22, 4, 'Data Sovereignty', 'How mature is your government''s data governance capability?', 'No formal data catalogue or quality management across government', 'Some departments have data governance; no whole-of-government framework', 'Whole-of-government data strategy with cataloguing and access controls', 'Mature data governance: real-time cataloguing, quality management, stewardship roles', 10, 35, 65, 90),
