(24, 5, 'Directed Intelligence Maturity', 'To what extent are national AI deployments tied to explicit sovereign priorities?', 'AI deployments are opportunistic with no link to national strategy', 'Some AI projects reference national priorities but most are ad hoc', 'AI deployments are systematically mapped to sovereign priority areas', 'Mission-first AI: sovereign priorities drive technology selection, not the reverse', 10, 35, 65, 90),
